* '''[[Greek Orthodox Church of Jerusalem|Patriarchate of Jerusalem]]''' (''Patriarch of the Holy City of Jerusalem and all Holy Land, Syria, Arabia, beyond the Jordan River, Cana of Galilee, and Sacred Zion'')
